data.description: WOW- kitchen got a facelift and other fantastic improvements! If you saw us before you really need to check us out!! This Charming home in the popular area of Cameron Ranch wants to make a new buyer so happy! This wonderful house is now for its new owner to put some personal touches and make it their HOME! Everyone will appreciate the large kitchen, overlooking the private yard, as it features an abundance of Granite counter space,  and ALL SS appliances included! Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and a loft with newer LVP flooring!
